本游戏一经发售，就被批评声所淹没，并被评为“{{tsl|en|List of video games notable for negative reception|史上最烂的游戏}}”。Game Rankings依据网站上的5个评论，给予游戏50.90%的汇总评价，The Electric Playground给予游戏4/10分的评价<ref name="gr"/>，同时《电子游戏月刊》给予游戏3.25/10分的评价<ref name="gr"/>。[[Gametrailers|Gametrailers]]将游戏命名为“史上第八烂的电子游戏”，并称之为“高质量作品的廉价模仿”，因本游戏发行时间与《马里奥64》相近，所以借此话来讽刺本游戏乃《马里奥64》的“抄袭版”<ref name="gamasutra"/><ref name="gt"/>。脱口秀主持人史葛·鲁宾（Scott Rubin）称本游戏为“可怕的克隆作品”。他们描述游戏画面就跟“涂上颜色的纸板箱”一样，还批评大笨猫所说的俏皮话<ref name="gt">{{cite web |author=Nov 17, 2006 |url=http://www.gametrailers.com/video/top-ten-gt-countdown/15147 |title=GT Countdown Video Game, Top Ten Best And Worst Games Of All Time | Video Clip | Game Trailers & Videos |publisher=GameTrailers.com |date=2006-11-17 |accessdate=2010-10-19 |archive-date=2011-01-28 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/5w3redfNk?url=http://www.gametrailers.com/video/top-ten-gt-countdown/15147 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[GamesRadar|GamesRadar]]的汤姆·古尔特（Tom Goulter）认为《大笨猫3D》作为电子游戏，就如同糟糕的电影《[[地球战场|地球战场]]》或是《[[外太空九号计划|外太空九号计划]]》一样<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gamesradar.com/f/gamings-would-be-innovators/a-2009091695122763015 |title=Gaming's would-be innovators |publisher=GamesRadar |date= |accessdate=2010-10-19 |archive-date=2011-06-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110615224411/http://www.gamesradar.com/f/gamings-would-be-innovators/a-2009091695122763015 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。{{tsl|en|seanbaby|肖恩·贝比}}（Seanbaby）将游戏命名为“第十七烂的游戏”，他对游戏的操纵感、角色性格以及视觉效果，只能用“该死”来形容。他另补充一句：“你几乎可以感觉到游戏制作者有多憎恨美国的孩子。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.seanbaby.com/nes/egm17.htm |title=EGM's Crapstravaganza: The 20 Worst Games of All Time |publisher=Seanbaby.com |date= |accessdate=2010-10-19 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101008183748/http://www.seanbaby.com/nes/egm17.htm |archivedate=2010-10-08 }}</ref>”

IGN的戴维·泽德寇（David Zdyrko）称游戏为“永恒经典的覆灭”<ref>{{cite web |author=David Zdyrko |url=http://ps2.ign.com/articles/166/166437p1.html |title=Frogger: The Great Quest - PlayStation 2 Review at IGN |publisher=Ps2.ign.com |date=2001-11-30 |accessdate=2010-10-19 |archive-date=2011-05-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110525051945/http://ps2.ign.com/articles/166/166437p1.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。同处IGN的利维·布坎南（Levi Buchanan）将本游戏当做尝试二维过渡至三维却失败的明显例子，他主要批评其操纵感及角色设计，并指出游戏角色的外貌与个性均使前作走向毁灭<ref>{{cite web |last=Buchanan |first=Levi |url=http://retro.ign.com/articles/928/928126p1.html |title=What Hath Sonic Wrought?, Vol. 1 - Retro Feature at IGN |publisher=Retro.ign.com |date=2008-11-07 |accessdate=2010-10-19 |archive-date=2010-08-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100802025551/http://retro.ign.com/articles/928/928126p1.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。总体来说，他们都不怎么喜欢本游戏<ref>{{cite web|author= Marc Nix |url=http://psp.ign.com/articles/775/775271p1.html |title=The Future of PSP - SCE Bend - PlayStation Portable Feature at IGN |publisher=Psp.ign.com |date=2007-03-23 |accessdate=2010-10-19}}</ref>。IGN指出，人们普遍认为这是史上最糟糕的游戏之一<ref>{{cite web |url=http://uk.games.ign.com/top-100-game-creators/supergreen/79.html |title=IGN - 79. Marc Blank |publisher=Uk.games.ign.com |date= |accessdate=2010-10-19 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110713005431/http://uk.games.ign.com/top-100-game-creators/supergreen/79.html |archivedate=2011-07-13 }}</ref>。[[1UP.com|1UP.com]]称本游戏很“可怜”，同时也是“潜在的马里奥杀手”<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.1up.com/do/feature?cId=3135642 |title=The Essential 50 Part 37: Tomb Raider from |publisher=1UP.com |date= |accessdate=2010-10-19 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060505222837/http://www.1up.com/do/feature?cId=3135642 |archivedate=2006-05-05 }}</ref>。[[GamePro|GamePro]]称游戏为“吸金作品”<ref>{{cite web |last=Mike |first=Major |url=http://www.gamepro.com/article/features/23884/e3-2002-famous-mascots-get-a-major-makeover/ |title=E3 2002: Famous Mascots Get a Major Makeover, page 5, Feature Story from |publisher=GamePro |date=2002-05-30 |accessdate=2010-10-19 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/query?url=http://www.gamepro.com/article/features/23884/e3-2002-famous-mascots-get-a-major-makeover/&date=2011-11-30+19:00:13 |archivedate=2011-11-30 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。GameZone的Jkdmedia认为早期三维游戏就和本游戏一样，既黑暗又可怕<ref>{{cite web |author=Tyeise 6/27/10 5:31 PM   |url=http://nds.gamezone.com/reviews/item/m_m_s_adventure_nds_review/ |title=M&M's Adventure - NDS - Review | GameZone.com |publisher=Nds.gamezone.com |date= |accessdate=2010-10-19 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101028164637/http://nds.gamezone.com/reviews/item/m_m_s_adventure_nds_review/ |archivedate=2010-10-28 }}</ref>。他随后将本游戏与《[[象棋大师:学习的艺术|象棋大师:学习的艺术]]》（Chessmaster: The Art of Learning）的画质进行对比，之后得出这条评论：“《大笨猫3D》占了上风。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://nds.gamezone.com/reviews/item/chessmaster_the_art_of_learning_nds_review/ |title=Chessmaster: The Art of Learning - NDS - Review | GameZone.com |publisher=Nds.gamezone.com |date= |accessdate=2010-10-19 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120710105147/http://nds.gamezone.com/reviews/item/chessmaster_the_art_of_learning_nds_review/ |archivedate=2012-07-10 }}</ref>”[[Kotaku|Kotaku]]的迈克尔·梅科阔特（Michael McWhertor）称未发布的游戏《吃豆人鬼区》较《超级马里奥64》来说更接近于本游戏<ref>{{cite web |url=http://kotaku.com/5421097/the-making-and-death-of-pac+man-ghost-zone |title=The Making And Death Of Pac-Man Ghost Zone |publisher=Kotaku.com |date=2009-12-07 |accessdate=2010-10-19 |archive-date=2010-05-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100527221247/http://kotaku.com/5421097/the-making-and-death-of-pac+man-ghost-zone |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

然而，尽管游戏大多受负面评价，Absolute PlayStation却给予本游戏67%的评价<ref name="AbsPS"/>。[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]本不看好本游戏，却给予游戏5.5/10分的“一般”评价<ref name="GSpot"/>。{{tsl|en|DieHard GameFan}}和{{tsl|en|Next Generation}}亦予以游戏相当好的评价<ref name="GFAQs"/>。

PSExtreme给予游戏93%的评价，并授予游戏“金X奖”（Gold X Award），此奖在游戏封面上亦有明显体现。由于杂志并不出名，曾有错误的传言称这个杂志和这个奖都是骗人的，Accolade也轻而易举地把他们当做促销本游戏的好方式<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.psextreme.com/ratings.htm#GOLD |title=EXcavate: Rating (Highest to Lowest) |publisher=PSExtreme |date= |accessdate=2016-03-20 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/19970601104334/http://www.psextreme.com/ratings.htm#GOLD |archivedate=1997-06-01 }}</ref>
。

==可能的后续作品==
2015年，开发人员宣布大笨猫系列的前两作将可在[[Steam|Steam]]上发售。游戏的程序员同时也张贴出募集游戏角色粉丝的请愿书。如果成功的话，他们可能会制作新的大笨猫系列游戏<ref>{{cite web |url=https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=553404370 |title=Steam Greenlight :: BUBSY Two-Fur - Steam Community |publisher=[[Steam_(software)|Steam]] |date=2015-11-16 |accessdate=2015-11-27 |archive-date=2015-12-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208055100/https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=553404370 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

